            <p class='section-desc'>Whether it is 10 years or one minute ago, data can be queried just by specifying the time range. Data can be aggregated over time, over multiple time streams or both. Ad Hoc queries or analyses can be executed via the TDengine shell, Python, R or Matlab.</p>
