            <h2 class='section-item-title'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" width='32' height='32' ><path d="M160 48v224h64v192l128-256h-64l64-160H160z"/></svg>Zero Management, No Learning Curve</h2>
            <p class='section-desc'>It takes only seconds to download, install, and run it successfully; there are no other dependencies. Automatic partitioning on tables or DBs. Standard SQL is adopted, together with C/C++, Python, JDBC, Go, RESTful, and Node.JS connectors.</p>
